            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>BBQ sauce</strong> and<strong> half</strong> your<strong> smoked sea salt</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce is slightly reduced</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1684236523066-x200.jpg",
