            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1684236530443-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1684236530443-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1684236530443-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1684236530443-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the<strong> warmed hot dog bun</strong> with the <strong>BBQ pulled mushrooms</strong>, then top with most of your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> to the side and sprinkle the<strong> remaining smoked sea salt</strong> on top – these are your <strong>smoked salt chips</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>dressed lettuce wedges</strong> to the side and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
